# Part 2

## Describe a bicycle/motorcycle/car trip you would like to go on.

One trip I’ve always wanted to take is a long self-driving car trip across western China with a few close friends from university. We’ve talked about it many times, especially during stressful exam periods, because we all enjoy travelling and photography.

If I had the chance, I’d love to drive through places like Xinjiang, Qinghai, and Tibet. Those regions are famous for their breathtaking natural scenery, such as snow-covered mountains, grasslands, deserts, and huge lakes. I’ve seen many travel documentaries and online videos about those places, and the landscapes look almost unreal.

I think the best time to go would probably be during summer vacation, because the weather would be more comfortable and we’d have enough free time for a long journey. Since the trip would probably last over a week, we could stop whenever we wanted, explore small towns, try local food, and enjoy the scenery slowly instead of rushing from one tourist attraction to another.

The reason I specifically want to travel by car is the sense of freedom it gives. Compared with planes or trains, driving allows people to be much more flexible. For example, if we discovered a beautiful lake or sunset along the road, we could simply stop and enjoy the moment. I also think road trips create stronger memories because you spend a lot of time talking, listening to music, and sharing experiences with your friends during the journey.

Another reason is that I really enjoy the atmosphere of travelling on the road. I can imagine us driving through huge open landscapes while listening to music and watching the scenery change gradually outside the window. To me, that sounds far more meaningful than simply arriving at a destination quickly.

Overall, I think it would not only be a relaxing holiday, but also an unforgettable life experience.

---

### 中文翻译：

我一直很想进行的一次旅行，是和几个大学好朋友一起去中国西部进行一次长途自驾游。我们在考试压力特别大的时候，经常聊到这个计划，因为大家都喜欢旅行和摄影。

如果有机会的话，我特别想开车去新疆、青海和西藏这些地方。那些地区以壮观的自然风景闻名，比如雪山、草原、沙漠以及巨大的湖泊。我看过很多纪录片和网上的视频，那些风景看起来几乎像电影一样。

我觉得最适合去的时间应该是暑假，因为天气会更舒服，而且我们也有足够长的时间进行这种长途旅行。因为整个旅程可能持续一周以上，所以我们可以随时停车、探索小城镇、尝试当地食物，而不是像普通旅游那样赶时间。

我之所以特别想选择开车旅行，是因为它会给人一种自由感。和飞机或火车相比，自驾会更加灵活。比如如果路上突然看到特别美的湖泊或者夕阳，我们就可以直接停下来慢慢欣赏。

另外，我觉得公路旅行更容易留下深刻回忆，因为一路上你会和朋友聊天、听音乐、分享经历。我甚至能想象我们一边开车，一边听歌，看着窗外风景慢慢变化。我觉得这种体验，比单纯快速到达目的地更有意义。

总的来说，我认为这不仅会是一次放松的假期，更会是一段难忘的人生经历。

